==English==

===Pronunciation===
* ''[[RP]]:'' {{IPA|/ˈstɒkɪŋ/}}

===Noun===
{{en-noun-reg}}

# A soft [[garment]] worn on the [[foot]] and [[lower leg]], usually [[knit]] or [[woven]], worn under [[shoe]]s or other [[footwear]].
#: ''A pair of stockings.''
# Something like or [[suggest]]ing such a garment.

====Usage notes====
*'''stocking''' may refer either to men's socks or to women's [[hose]], but rarely to socks when worn by women.  However, this usage appears somewhat variable.

====Derived terms====
* [[bluestocking]]
* [[in one's stockinged feet]], [[in one's stockings]] or [[in one's stocking-feet]]
* [[stockinger]]
* [[stocking filler]]
* [[stocking-maker]]
* [[stocking stuffer]]

